{"tid":1631750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實你地知唔知乜撚野叫成效","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:46:14.000Z","uid":306172,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6df03e8f008afb7947a4ad63f6d3894eace8a412","tid":1631750,"uid":306172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:13:59.000Z","msg":"做任何行動都好<br />\n最重要既係幫到我地成功爭取民主呀！！<br />\n我地所有既成效都係base on呢樣野<br />\n唔係遊幾多次行 拆幾多間鋪就等於高成效<br />\n就等於有助我地達成目標架<br />\n做錯野係可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">負成效</span></span>架<br />\n所以大家坐低一兩日思考方向係咪咁撚難？<br />\n<br />\n成效分做兩樣<br />\n一樣係爭取國際支持<br />\n一樣係威脅到港府同老共<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該做全部任何行動之前諗清楚<br />\n做果樣野係有冇撚用既<br />\n保持返警覺性<br />\n</span></span><br />\n仲有<br />\n唔撚好再起到日撚日互屌得唔撚得<br />\n重要文宣又唔撚推<br />\n國際戰線twitter又唔撚推<br />\n冇文宣有乜撚成效呀<br />\n做咁多野有乜撚野用呀"},{"pid":"a22a9304ad58b433cfe8da814df0aabd6273680c","tid":1631750,"uid":306172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:14:38.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到"},{"pid":"33da05593cc313dd6785fbe504d6f331f9543be2","tid":1631750,"uid":136221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:15:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">善用Twitter Hashtags</span>"},{"pid":"9d030a28128b3b86a3e39196b74c44c63e7e0952","tid":1631750,"uid":136221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:16:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">利申twitter好多正野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"aabbae4cbc3baa1cddb11a3eb537bb7b31496e4d","tid":1631750,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:16:47.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n你應承過會做勇武塊盾<br />\n宜家勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勿中林鄭割蓆計！</span></strong></span><br />\n記唔記得當初應承過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈都唔割</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣洗地</span></strong></span>開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b1e423d5f09929ecd80d07d4ab1b38b135aa5f5a","tid":1631750,"uid":287629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:16:47.000Z","msg":"呢幾日一定有手足上咗腦，唔覺意做咗啲過火野<br />\n我地唔好忘記，香港廣大市民（除咗啲無得救既死藍絲外）係我地既同伴，有朝一日，他們甚至會變成我地既手足<br />\n大家做野之餘，有啲野錯就要認。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n是時候道歉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1631703/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1631703/page/1?post=1</a>"},{"pid":"158fbd237ee1cfddddb303d32ecff24f91707904","tid":1631750,"uid":136221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:18:23.000Z","msg":"不分化 不指責 做得唔好真係要檢討 <br />\n今晚嘅手足不是condom <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">快閃！！！&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;遊行</span>"},{"pid":"ab6409668c634ef36952eea232ae091155e82edf","tid":1631750,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5107e3cfd0aa0dce44ba92410411b03902cb0e1","tid":1631750,"uid":320494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:25:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"157a4d7d1835ba536d13fff7270cdf070335fa4e","tid":1631750,"uid":298767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:26:02.000Z","msg":"推唔郁都照推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eef4d3e4fe71755d74e5ce5f76e136c074a7420","tid":1631750,"uid":57438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:31:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb95db97a2a29baf854db54117646e6d992a5601","tid":1631750,"uid":57438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:32:14.000Z","msg":"勇武大家想保護你國際有後援<br />\n<br />\n國際輸左保送武勇去老美嘅後路都斷"},{"pid":"9c7239ece25dac1bc23759f6d0809a6fa73f1705","tid":1631750,"uid":68261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:36:48.000Z","msg":"唔該冷靜下自己反思下行動有冇效，可唔可以達到我地想要既目標先得架"},{"pid":"bcf035bcbf3e87b686be625a144a1cddbe288628","tid":1631750,"uid":195924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:38:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a6391394ce05f603ac01524e5ba63470585cb9ff","tid":1631750,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"81a85a11b6ea06e8474a311578affcadb6c1165c","tid":1631750,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:40:46.000Z","msg":"有道理 重要野要緊<br />\n不過樓豬咪又係屌鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b1b419eedead99634a152753899228e2107612","tid":1631750,"uid":153258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb95db97a2a29baf854db54117646e6d992a5601","tid":1631750,"uid":57438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:32:14.000Z","msg":"勇武大家想保護你國際有後援<br />\n<br />\n國際輸左保送武勇去老美嘅後路都斷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:06.000Z","msg":"［和理非可做的事］可以和理非，但不能不勇武<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631884\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631884</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"34eaf1bb6e97e00473aa17f08b35d192136572df","tid":1631750,"uid":300559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:15:29.000Z","msg":"Support <br />\nbe clever<br />\nbe brave<br />\nbe WATER!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<strong>智仁勇!!!!!!!</strong>"},{"pid":"f688d99d47616d93ecedb0914956a26d463314c8","tid":1631750,"uid":17801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:18:55.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b9f4e7fc8cd40999768a53eb0c7846b982040628","tid":1631750,"uid":204691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81a85a11b6ea06e8474a311578affcadb6c1165c","tid":1631750,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:40:46.000Z","msg":"有道理 重要野要緊<br />\n不過樓豬咪又係屌鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:29:34.000Z","msg":"岩啊 屌佢個閪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係好似啲人講 屌你老母臭閪我成世人最撚憎人講粗口架啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc754e5446976a21079b1e35a0fcff27076627b5","tid":1631750,"uid":306172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9f4e7fc8cd40999768a53eb0c7846b982040628","tid":1631750,"uid":204691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81a85a11b6ea06e8474a311578affcadb6c1165c","tid":1631750,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:40:46.000Z","msg":"有道理 重要野要緊<br />\n不過樓豬咪又係屌鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:29:34.000Z","msg":"岩啊 屌佢個閪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係好似啲人講 屌你老母臭閪我成世人最撚憎人講粗口架啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:42:48.000Z","msg":"小弟想叫大家做番重要野<br />\n唔好哂時間互屌姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\